      'Listeriolysin O (LLO): Escapes phagosome, cholesterol-dependent',
      'Crosses three barriers: Intestinal, blood-brain, placental',
      'Most dangerous in pregnancy (3rd trimester), neonates, elderly, immunocompromised',
