      'Diphtheria toxin encoded by β-corynephage (tox gene)',
      'Toxin mechanism: ADP-ribosylates EF-2 → inhibits protein synthesis',
      'Only lysogenized strains are toxigenic',
      'Pseudomembrane: Grey-white, adherent, BLEEDS on removal',
